item.content:encoded:
MC David Tennis Elbow Support
Features Velcro® cinch strap for direct pressure. Commonly used for tennis elbow problems. 25,5cm contoured thermal neoprene sleeve completely covers elbow, and has nylon facing on both sides. Heavy duty nylon on outer side for durability.

Available sizes: S, M, L, XL.

S 20-24cm
M 24-28cm
L 28-30cm
XL 30-35cm

item.content:encoded:
Stanno Elite Sock Unisex

The Stanno Elite stocking is made of high-quality Marfil Active and Marfil Shingo yarns. The Marfil Active yarns ensure high elasticity and a perfect fit. The high-quality Marfil Shingo yarns in the footbed ensure a good transport of the bodily fluids and give a comfortable feeling. The stocking is ideal for indoor sports and tennis.

SKU: 442103-8000
